sub_title: Business Excellence Manager North Europe - Sanofi Genzyme
summary: Passionate about science and biology, I have always been guided by my curiosity. From my scientific background and my experiences in research lab, I have developed my perseverance and an analytical mind. Then, I went to ESSEC Business School to explore the current knowledge on Project Management. All these experiences help me today on my recent jobs related to data analysis to support businesses in healthcare, internally or externally.
